cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.CV 

The paper focuses on evaluating the impact of impairments on user engagement in the context of video streaming, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper introduces new metrics to assess user engagement, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the analysis involves assessing the impact of impairments on video quality, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV).
